::Mosquitor::

Mosquitor, already damaged from his battle with Prowl, smashes into a boulder from Dinobot's shots. He struggles to his feet, using the boulder for cover.

Standing up and yelling in rage, Mosquitor jumps again at Dinobot, again firing more acid.
